    "Broadly enabling such fine-tuning substantially increases the breadth of model capabilities and associated difficulties in predicting or constraining model behaviors.",
    "This open-endedness is challenging because it means AI developers may deploy their systems without fully knowing potentially unexpected (and possibly harmful) behaviors in response to un-tested inputs.",
